name: American Ninja Warrior Obstacles
content:
Description: list of all American Ninja Warrior Obstacles in Seasons 1-10

[Source](https://data.world/ninja/anw-obstacle-history )

Processing: data was already in a clean format, a few column titles were changed

Columns:

* Season (numerical): what season the obstacle appeared in
* Location (string): city or region of the season
* Round/Stage (string): round or stage that the obstacle appeared in
* Obstacle Name (string): official name of the obstacle
* Order (numerical): the order the obstacle appeared in during the challenge
